# =============================================================================
# TrAIding Floor — optional integrations
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to user-data/.env and uncomment what you want enabled.
# Every section is independent — the floor runs fine with all of it commented
# out (deterministic strategies only, no LLM, no Dune, no Telegram).
#
#   mkdir -p user-data
#   curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/traidingfloor/install/main/.env.example -o user-data/.env
#   # edit user-data/.env, then:
#   docker compose restart
# =============================================================================

# ─── Hyperliquid credentials (required to place real trades) ─────────────────
# Generate at https://app.hyperliquid.xyz → API. The wallet you authorise here
# is the only one the agent can sign with. Use a sub-account, not your main.
# HL_WALLET_ADDRESS=0x...
# HL_API_SECRET=...

# ─── LLM reviewer + agent chat (optional) ────────────────────────────────────
# Without this, the floor runs deterministic strategies + rule-based head
# trader only. With it, you get the Phase-2 LLM second-opinion reviewer
# and the cockpit chat. Anthropic API key (not Claude.ai login):
# https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─── Dune Analytics intel sidecar (optional) ─────────────────────────────────
# Polls cross-venue arb signals, alt-coin funding map, and a whale leaderboard
# every 10 min. POSTs the brief to the head trader, which folds it into
# decisions and the LLM context. Without DUNE_API_KEY the sidecar exits
# cleanly. Get a free key at https://dune.com/settings/api
# DUNE_API_KEY=...

# ─── Telegram alerts (optional) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# The watcher sidecar posts to a Telegram chat when:
#   - daily PnL drops more than DRAWDOWN_PCT_TRIP (default 10%)
#   - fill rate drops below FILL_RATE_TRIP (default 30%)
#   - the agent process dies
#   - every HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_H hours (default 4)
# Setup (4 min): create a bot via @BotFather, get the token, message your bot
# once, then fetch the chat ID from
# https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=1234567890:AAH-...
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789

# ─── Watcher tuning (optional — defaults shown) ──────────────────────────────
# WATCHER_POLL_SEC=60
# HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_H=4
# DRAWDOWN_PCT_TRIP=10.0
# FILL_RATE_TRIP=0.30
# ALERT_COOLDOWN_SEC=900
